<br />
Which is why I stipulated all other things being equal.  And chances of two people being put on the list at exactly the same time are too high to make the issue a point.  Chances of two candidates being exactly equal are as well, imo.  I don't think that kind of problem is one that requires worrying about.  In any event, I'm definitely not going to say that just because someone is younger, they are more deserving.
                  
